I wanna let it run out of gas.

826
01:02:41,995 --> 01:02:44,429
我不想那老头子醉驾
I don't want the bastard drivin' drunk.

827
01:02:44,498 --> 01:02:46,864
他时常都是醉酒
He's drunk all the time now.

828
01:02:46,933 --> 01:02:49,902
我们要把车钥匙藏起来
After, we'll hide the keys.

829
01:02:49,970 --> 01:02:52,370
枪击事件有新进展吗？汤比利
Anything new about
the shooting? Twombley?

830
01:02:52,439 --> 01:02:56,000
没有　我想只是大家所想的意外
No. I guess it was an accident
like everybody thinks.

831
01:02:56,076 --> 01:02:58,636
想要听听我的想法吗？
Want to know what
I think happened?

832
01:02:58,712 --> 01:03:01,374
到处都找到这些东西
You find them everywhere.

833
01:03:01,448 --> 01:03:04,884
我想你对枪击的第一反应是对的
I think your first response
to the shooting was the correct one.

834
01:03:15,295 --> 01:03:19,732
是什么？那不是意外
- Which is?
- That it wasn't an accident.

835
01:03:19,800 --> 01:03:21,768
那是谁开的枪？
Well, then who shot him?

836
01:03:21,835 --> 01:03:24,429
你的朋友，杰克.赫特
Your friend, I think. Jack Hewitt.

837
01:03:24,504 --> 01:03:26,438
杰克
Jack.

838
01:03:26,506 --> 01:03:29,066
少来，鲁夫，他有什么动机
Come on, Rolfe.
Give me a motive.

839
01:03:29,142 --> 01:03:31,906
钱　钱？谁来给他钱
- Money.
- Money? Who'd pay 'im
that kind of money?

840
01:03:31,978 --> 01:03:35,311
不是黑帮，他们有自己的人动手，都是职业杀手
Not the mob.
They got their own guys. Specialists.

841
01:03:35,382 --> 01:03:40,012
汤比利豁然死了，谁会从中得益
Who else benefits
if Twombley is suddenly dead?

842
01:03:42,889 --> 01:03:46,086
我不知道，你来告诉我吧
- I don't know. You tell me.
- Okay.

843
01:03:46,159 --> 01:03:51,358
有人不想汤比利去作证
It's likely there are people
in the union who don't want
Twombley to testify.

844
01:03:51,431 --> 01:03:54,491
可能包括他的女婿，副总裁
