and will probably be
the next president.

846
01:03:57,170 --> 01:04:00,333
我在报纸上看到的　他叫什么名字了　美乔丹？
- I read that in the papers.
Uh, what's his name?
- Mel Gordon.

847
01:04:00,407 --> 01:04:03,103
梅尔.乔丹　那家伙开宝马车对吧？
- Mel Gordon, right.
- The guy in the B.M.W., right?

848
01:04:03,176 --> 01:04:05,701
是的　我的道理是
Okay, here's my theory.

849
01:04:05,779 --> 01:04:08,976
汤比利他不知道非法借贷
Twombley, he doesn't know
about illegal loans or whatever,

850
01:04:09,049 --> 01:04:13,543
