He wants it to look like an accident.

854
01:04:24,397 --> 01:04:26,922
打猎意外
A hunting accident's perfect.

855
01:04:27,000 --> 01:04:29,798
你在树林里射杀人　
Around here,
you shoot somebody in the woods,

856
