I care about what happened.

869
01:05:18,818 --> 01:05:21,616
事件的真相
The truth.

870
01:05:21,688 --> 01:05:26,921
记得我是学历史的
Remember, I'm a student
of history. Books.

871
01:05:36,970 --> 01:05:39,905
