I agreed to everything
that she said.

909
01:09:09,382 --> 01:09:12,215
我只是想她喜欢我
I just wanted her to like me.

910
01:09:12,285 --> 01:09:14,981
我想做个好父亲
I wanted to be a good father.

911
01:09:16,523 --> 01:09:19,549
我有份文件
I have the documents.

912
01:09:19,626 --> 01:09:22,288
你知道吗
You know,

913
01:09:22,362 --> 01:09:26,230
如果你结婚后　你工作的时候家里有个人，对你很有帮助
It would help if you were married,
if there was someone at home
while you're at work.

914
01:09:26,299 --> 01:09:29,564
我很快计划好
I plan to soon.

915
01:09:29,636 --> 01:09:31,831
多快？
How soon?

916
01:09:31,905 --> 01:09:35,136
下个春天　
- Next spring.
- It would help...

917
01:09:35,208 --> 01:09:38,177
环境上有些改变是会有所帮助
if there was some change in circumstance
since this was drawn,

918
01:09:38,244 --> 01:09:44,046
如果你的前妻有吸毒　酗酒　
if there was some drug or alcohol abuse
on the part of your ex-wife.

919
01:09:44,117 --> 01:09:47,109
性问题会影响你的孩子　不好意思
Sexual problems upsetting the child.
I'm sorry!

920
01:09:47,187 --> 01:09:51,954
这些事我一定要解释清楚　我们要讨论这份文件
But these are the things
we're gonna have to explore
if we want to contest this document.

921
01:09:54,828 --> 01:09:59,162
一定要那么乱吗？绝对要
- Does it have to get that messy?
- Absolutely.

922
01:09:59,232 --> 01:10:02,133
这只是冰山一角　维候斯先生
This is just the tip of the iceberg,
Mr. Whitehouse.

923
01:10:02,202 --> 01:10:05,968
我希望你明白我说的意思
I hope you understand
what I'm saying.

924
01:10:06,039 --> 01:10:08,303
看来没什么希望是吗？
Looks kind of hopeless, don't it?

925
01:10:08,374 --> 01:10:11,673
不　我要看看离婚法令
No, not really. I'll have
another look at the divorce decree,

926
01:10:11,744 --> 01:10:14,508
看是否我们可以改正
see if we can get it redrawn.

927
01:10:14,581 --> 01:10:18,108
但是有几点我要采访你的女儿
