to have to interview your daughter.

928
01:10:18,184 --> 01:10:21,620
叫吉尔是吧？是的
- It's Jill, right?
- Yes.

929
01:10:21,688 --> 01:10:23,622
你有烟灰缸吗？
You got an ashtray?

930
01:10:29,495 --> 01:10:32,953
