I know. The custody thing wasn't
just my trying to get back at her.

939
01:11:06,332 --> 01:11:09,392
我也不是那么笨
I'm not as dumb as I look.

940
01:11:09,469 --> 01:11:12,563
我没说你笨
I didn't say you
looked dumb, Mr. Whitehouse.

941
01:11:15,675 --> 01:11:18,838
我爱我的女儿　我会给你五百块
I love my daughter.
I'll send you the $500.

942
01:11:23,650 --> 01:11:26,084
不好意思，午餐吃了太久
I'm sorry about the long lunch.

943
01:11:26,152 --> 01:11:28,120
