My transmission's going out again.

944
01:11:28,187 --> 01:11:31,645
你有想过拥有部新车吗
Did you ever think about
getting a new car?

945
01:11:31,724 --> 01:11:34,124
你会约我钱吗
On what you pay me?

946
01:11:36,129 --> 01:11:39,292
