我要做什么？不用
- What do I have to do for it?
- Nothing.

955
01:12:07,060 --> 01:12:09,358
韦德　我考虑过了
You know, Wade,
I've been thinking.

956
01:12:09,429 --> 01:12:12,330
你在附近还不够受欢迎
You don't get enough
appreciation around here.

957
01:12:12,398 --> 01:12:17,028
我早上看见梅尔.乔丹来这里　怎样？
- Uh-uh. I saw Mel Gordon
in here this morning.
- So?

958
01:12:17,103 --> 01:12:21,767
他说了我要给他传票的事吗？那家伙不接受
He say anything about
that summons I tried to give him?
Son of a bitch wouldn't accept it.

959
01:12:21,841 --> 01:12:23,809
韦德　那家伙不够聪明
- Wade, "dat" wasn't smart.
- "That?"

960
01:12:23,876 --> 01:12:26,936
在他岳父打死自己之后出来
Going out right after
the man's father-in-law shot himself.

961
01:12:27,013 --> 01:12:30,676

It's pronounced "that,"
not "dat." That.

962
01:12:30,750 --> 01:12:33,548

- That.
- Yeah.

963
01:12:33,619 --> 01:12:36,918
不要说这个了　帮我个忙
