Call it a favor to me.

964
01:12:36,990 --> 01:12:38,924
你？为什么　
You? Why?

965
01:12:38,992 --> 01:12:41,517
梅尔和我做生意
Well, Mel's doing
some business with me.

966
01:12:41,594 --> 01:12:44,119
