979
01:15:22,121 --> 01:15:26,490
绝妙打猎意外事故
A hunting accident's perfect.

980
01:15:26,559 --> 01:15:28,720
枪击事件有进展吗
Anything new
about the shooting?

981
01:15:28,794 --> 01:15:30,819
我想你对事件第一反应是对的
I think your first response
to the shooting was the correct one.

982
01:15:30,897 --> 01:15:33,422
你的朋友　杰克赫特
Your friend, I think. Jack Hewitt.
He's my favorite.

983
01:15:33,499 --> 01:15:36,900
钱　打猎意外　我想不是意外
Money. Hunting accident.
I bet it wasn't an accident.

984
01:15:36,969 --> 01:15:39,631
不是我　我不在　真相...
It wasn't me. I wasn't there.
- The truth.

985
01:15:39,705 --> 01:15:43,266
记住事情发生跟你说的不一样　
Remember, it may have happened,
but not the way you said.

986
01:15:43,342 --> 01:15:47,005
太完美就是有漏洞
It's what happened
not because it's neat.

987
01:15:51,584 --> 01:15:55,680
汤比利突然死亡就是谋杀
Twombley's sudden death.
Killing was the correct one.

988
01:15:55,755 --> 01:15:57,689
真相　记住..
The truth, remember.

989
01:16:25,451 --> 01:16:30,081
你疯了　差点要了我们俩的命
You crazy son of a bitch!
You almost killed us both!

990
01:16:30,156 --> 01:16:32,317
你快滚
Get off the fuckin' ice!

991
01:16:32,391 --> 01:16:34,518
滚
Get off!

992
01:16:38,764 --> 01:16:40,732
你们去干嘛　杰克
What're you runnin' from, Jack?

993
01:16:42,435 --> 01:16:44,369
我们要谈谈
We're gonna talk.

994
01:16:52,378 --> 01:16:55,575
退后　不然我会开枪的
Stay back. I'll shoot you.

995
01:16:55,648 --> 01:16:59,414
如果你不跑进车里　我就杀了你
I'll fuckin' shoot you dead
if you don't get back in that truck.

996
01:16:59,485 --> 01:17:02,579
你不会开枪的　放下枪
You ain't shootin' shit.
Now put the gun away.

997
01:17:02,655 --> 01:17:04,520
告诉我怎么回事
Tell me what happened.

998
01:17:04,590 --> 01:17:09,027
别动　你再动开枪打死你
Don't move!
I'll shoot you dead if you move.

999
01:18:31,477 --> 01:18:33,570

Thanks a lot.

1000
01:18:46,158 --> 01:18:48,092
住手
Stop that!

1001
01:18:48,160 --> 01:18:51,186
谁？我？我什么都没做啊
Who? Me?
I didn't do nothin'.

1002
01:18:54,467 --> 01:18:56,833
看我的杰作
Just look what a good job I done here.

1003
01:18:56,902 --> 01:19:00,167
你什么都没做　我应该把你留在家里
You haven't done anything. I should've
left you at home to stew in your drink.

1004
01:19:00,239 --> 01:19:02,173
让你喝醉　你应该这样
Damn right you should have.

1005
01:19:03,909 --> 01:19:05,843
时间问题
It's about time.

1006
01:19:05,911 --> 01:19:08,471
你父亲来了　玛格要照顾他
Your father's here.
Marge got to baby-sit him.

1007
01:19:08,547 --> 01:19:10,811
她跟你搬进来？
She moved in with you, huh?

1008
01:19:10,883 --> 01:19:14,341

- What happened?
- Don't even ask.

1009
01:19:14,420 --> 01:19:16,980
浪子
My, my, my.
The prodigal son.

1010
01:19:17,056 --> 01:19:18,990
倒霉
About fuckin' time too.

1011
01:19:19,058 --> 01:19:21,856
我有份新工作　后勤工作　洗碗
I got me a new job.
Second cook and bottle washer.

1012
01:19:21,927 --> 01:19:24,293
爸爸　我们回家吧
Pop, for chrissake,
let's go home.

1013
01:19:24,363 --> 01:19:26,456
对不起　我的车开不动了
I'm sorry. I got waylaid.

1014
01:19:29,602 --> 01:19:31,729
你的车开不动
The hell you got waylaid.

1015
01:19:31,804 --> 01:19:35,467
看你冻成这样　老天
You follow your prick around
like it was your nose, for chrissake!

1016
01:19:35,541 --> 01:19:38,476
带他走
Can it, Whitehouse.
Get him out of here.

1017
01:19:38,544 --> 01:19:41,672
之前有趣　但我累了　我们回家
- It was funny at first, but I'm tired.
- Let's go home.

1018
01:19:41,747 --> 01:19:46,275
是哪个家？你家还是我家
What home is that?
Is that your home or my home?

1019
01:19:46,352 --> 01:19:49,810
你他妈这么狡猾，韦德
You're a fuckin' sly, Wade.

1020
01:19:49,889 --> 01:19:53,825
你妈死了　她再也不能给你找借口了
Now, your mom's dead. She can't
make any excuses for you anymore.

1021
01:19:53,893 --> 01:19:59,195
你要好好对我　
You've got to deal with me now.
No more sugar tit, sonny!

1022
01:19:59,265 --> 01:20:02,962
我们回家吧　不要再吵了
- For chrissake, Pop. Let's go home.
- Don't give me any of your lip.

1023
01:20:03,035 --> 01:20:05,560
快离开这里　我不能
- Get out of this fast.
- I can't.

1024
01:20:05,638 --> 01:20:07,572
你要推我吗？
Are you pushing me?

1025
01:20:11,143 --> 01:20:15,204
不要再推我
- Come on. My God.
- Don't push me!

1026
01:20:15,281 --> 01:20:18,580
你认为你能管我吗　快点吧
- You think you can take me now?
Just come on.
- Come on.

1027
01:20:18,651 --> 01:20:21,745
上车　有什么问题
- Just get in the car.
- What's the matter?

1028
01:20:21,821 --> 01:20:24,381
上车
Just get in the car.

1029
01:20:24,457 --> 01:20:27,688
上车　懦夫
- Get in. Just get in.
- Wimp!

1030
01:20:27,760 --> 01:20:30,490
为什么你长不大呢
Why don't you grow up?

1031
01:20:30,563 --> 01:20:32,997
你永远不活不了自己
You never could stand up
for yourself!

1032
01:20:33,065 --> 01:20:35,090
该死的
Goddamn it!

1033
01:20:35,167 --> 01:20:40,104
你一点都不明白　我希望你去死
- You could never understand
what it's about.
- I wish you'd die!

1034
01:20:40,172 --> 01:20:43,630
噢　住手
Oh, stop it!
Just stop it! Stop it!

1035
01:21:20,212 --> 01:21:23,181
鲁夫　我要看见你在镜子里面　
No shit, Rolfe.
I glanced up and there he was,

1036
01:21:23,249 --> 01:21:25,843
镜子里面却只看到我
only it was me.

1037
01:21:25,918 --> 01:21:29,012
好像我从来没见过自己
But it was like
I had never seen myself before.

1038
01:21:29,088 --> 01:21:32,524
一张陌生的面孔　很难解释
It was a stranger's face.
It's hard to explain.

1039
01:21:32,591 --> 01:21:38,393
你坐飞机飞走了　就像我坐了一夜
You fly on automatic pilot, like I was
doing all night, and you disappear.

1040
01:21:38,464 --> 01:21:42,798
然后看见你的身体　或是你的脸
Then you accidentally see your body,
or your face, or whatever,

1041
01:21:42,868 --> 01:21:46,929
你不知道它属于谁
and you don't know
who in the hell it belongs to.

1042
01:21:47,006 --> 01:21:49,133
很陌生　
Strange.

1043
01:21:49,208 --> 01:21:53,907
我知道是和我爸爸有关　我知道我和他都很生气
It's the business with the old man,
I know, and how incredibly
pissed I was at him,

1044
01:21:53,979 --> 01:21:58,939
追捕杰克赫特　那该死的车　还有玛格的不安
and chasing Jack Hewitt
and the goddamned truck,
not to mention Margie's being upset.

1045
01:21:59,018 --> 01:22:02,078
一波未平一波又起
One thing on top of another.

1046
01:22:02,154 --> 01:22:04,554
韦德　你没事吧
Wade, are you all right?

1047
01:22:04,623 --> 01:22:07,319
你要听着　你不会相信
You gotta hear this.
You won't believe it.

1048
01:22:07,393 --> 01:22:10,692
梅尔乔丹去拜访拉利维亚
Mel Gordon had come by
to visit LaRiviere.

1049
01:22:10,763 --> 01:22:13,231
他们在办公室里
So they're in the office.

1050
01:22:13,299 --> 01:22:16,826
梅尔乔丹认识到我已知道
Mel Gordon realized
that I was onto them.

1051
01:22:16,902 --> 01:22:19,496
梅尔想他可以收买我
Mel thinks he can buy me off.

1052
01:22:19,572 --> 01:22:22,666
但拉利维亚他知道不行
But LaRiviere,
he knew that wouldn't work.

1053
01:22:22,741 --> 01:22:26,700
梅尔乔丹能够收买拉利维亚
Mel Gordon may be able
to buy off LaRiviere. That's one thing.

1054
01:22:26,779 --> 01:22:29,111
但我不行
But not me.

1055
01:22:29,181 --> 01:22:34,517
杰克赫特怎么能搞到如此糟糕
How could a guy like Jack Hewitt
get into a mess like this?

1056
01:22:52,071 --> 01:22:54,767
咖啡　谢谢艾尔
- Coffee?
- Thank you, Alma.

1057
01:22:54,840 --> 01:22:58,298
你要加糖或牛奶吗　不　斋啡的就行
- You want milk and sugar?
- No, no. Black is fine.

1058
01:22:58,377 --> 01:23:01,073
我喜欢喝这样的
I like it this way.

1059
01:23:01,146 --> 01:23:03,637
你买了台新电脑是吗
You got yourself
a new computer, huh?

1060
01:23:03,716 --> 01:23:06,651
我把我的文件都存进去
I've been putting
all my files into it.

1061
01:23:11,190 --> 01:23:13,215
你还好吧　韦德
You all right, Wade?

1062
01:23:13,292 --> 01:23:17,626
我有颗烂牙　疼死我了
Yeah. I got this damn tooth.
It's killing me.

1063
01:23:19,598 --> 01:23:23,625
有些事情烦我　跟别人一样
Got a few things bugging me,
just like everybody else.

1064
01:23:23,702 --> 01:23:25,636
我没事
I'm okay.

1065
01:23:25,704 --> 01:23:28,332
我不是想多嘴
I don't mean to pry.

1066
01:23:29,908 --> 01:23:33,503
你妈的死我很遗憾　但是葬礼办得很好
I'm sorry about your mother.
It was a nice funeral.

1067
01:23:34,880 --> 01:23:36,905
事情已经过去了
It's over now.

1068
01:23:38,384 --> 01:23:40,716
艾尔
Alma,

1069
01:23:40,786 --> 01:23:44,586
我觉得这个镇上有些肮脏的事情
I think there's some dirty business
goin' on in this town.

1070
01:23:44,657 --> 01:23:46,852
我知道　总会有一些的
I know that.
There always has been.

1071
01:23:46,925 --> 01:23:51,760
不　这事比以往还要毒辣
No, no. I think this is a little worse
than you and I are used to.

1072
01:23:51,830 --> 01:23:56,199
我要谈的是谋杀案件
I'm talkin' about murder,
among other things.

1073
01:23:56,268 --> 01:23:59,260
谁？汤比利
- Who?
- Twombley. Evan Twombley.

1074
01:23:59,338 --> 01:24:01,363
联合公司老板被枪杀
The union boss official
who got shot.

1075
01:24:01,440 --> 01:24:03,840
有人谋杀了他　谁？
- Somebody murdered him.
- Who would...

1076
01:24:06,311 --> 01:24:10,577
你认识杰克赫特　和我一起工作的那个年轻人
You know Jack Hewitt,
the kid I work with?

1077
01:24:10,649 --> 01:24:14,244
我想是杰克杀了他
Well, I think Jack shot him.

1078
01:24:14,319 --> 01:24:18,551
你知道汤比利是梅尔乔丹的岳父
You know, Twombley was
the father-in-law of Mel Gordon.

1079
01:24:18,624 --> 01:24:20,854
拉利维亚的朋友
That's a friend of LaRiviere's.

1080
01:24:20,926 --> 01:24:23,861
还不清楚是什么关系
I don't know what
the connection is yet,

1081
01:24:23,929 --> 01:24:26,830
但拉利维亚要杰克带他去打猎
but LaRiviere had Jack
take him out hunting,

1082
01:24:26,899 --> 01:24:29,197
假装成意外
pretending it was an accident.

1083
01:24:31,537 --> 01:24:36,133
杰克说出真相　他可以无罪的
If Jack told the truth, he could
be free by the time he's my age.

1084
01:24:37,776 --> 01:24:40,210
有些事情比你想象的更简单
Sometimes things
are simpler than you think.

1085
01:24:40,279 --> 01:24:43,715
让我问你一个问题　你不相信我吗
- Let me ask you a question.
- You don't believe me?

1086
01:24:43,782 --> 01:24:46,910
关于杰克的事　不
About Jack? No.

1087
01:24:46,985 --> 01:24:50,853
你最近检查过你父亲农场的税单吗？
Have you checked out the tax bill
on your father's farm lately?

1088
01:24:54,293 --> 01:24:58,320
我知道他欠了两年了
Um, I know he's been due
for a couple of years.

1089
01:24:58,397 --> 01:25:02,333
如果有了保险金　我想把单给付了
I was thinkin' of paying it
when the insurance comes in.

1090
01:25:02,401 --> 01:25:05,165
有人愿意买吗？
Has anybody offered to buy it?

1091
01:25:05,237 --> 01:25:07,899
有　事实上是拉利维亚
Yeah. Matter of fact, LaRiviere.

1092
01:25:12,144 --> 01:25:15,841
这里都是去年全镇的地产交易
These are all
the real estate transactions
in this town for the last year.

1093
01:25:15,914 --> 01:25:21,318
大多数是无用土地　大多数都是小雇主
Most of it is unused land. Most of it is
for little more than back taxes owed.

1094
01:25:21,386 --> 01:25:23,377
莉莲怎么样了？
How's Lillian?

1095
01:25:23,455 --> 01:25:26,117
她很好
She's fine.

1096
01:25:26,191 --> 01:25:28,250
这是三年内的　
That's three years ago.

1097
01:25:28,327 --> 01:25:30,261
很不同是吗？
It's quite a difference, hmm?

1098
01:25:30,329 --> 01:25:33,765
北部发展协会是什么
What's the North Country
Development Association?

1099
01:25:33,832 --> 01:25:36,300
我检查过
Went down to Concord.
I checked it out.

1100
01:25:36,368 --> 01:25:38,302
梅尔乔丹是总裁
Mel Gordon is the president.

1101
01:25:38,370 --> 01:25:41,828
副总裁是乔丹拉利维亚
And the vice president
and treasurer is Gordon LaRiviere.

1102
01:25:41,907 --> 01:25:47,573
他们去年买下全部山头　花了三十六万四千美元
They're buying up the whole mountain.
$364,000 last year.

1103
01:25:47,646 --> 01:25:51,639
我相信那是拉利维亚的一小部分
I believe that's a little
outside of LaRiviere's league.

1104
01:25:51,717 --> 01:25:54,151
汤比利有牵涉吗　没有
- Is Twombley involved?
- No.

1105
01:25:57,322 --> 01:25:59,256
Hmm.

1106
01:26:00,793 --> 01:26:02,727
他一定是发现了
He must've found out.

1107
01:26:05,330 --> 01:26:07,730
他们一定是要除掉他
They had to get rid of him.

1108
01:26:07,800 --> 01:26:11,497
杰克该受指责
And Jack...
Jack will get blamed for it.

1109
01:26:11,570 --> 01:26:13,765
所有这些数据显示
All these figures show is that...

1110
01:26:13,839 --> 01:26:18,276
乔丹拉利维亚很快就会很富有　因为他是镇长
Gordon LaRiviere is gonna be a very rich
man because of his being a selectman.

1111
01:26:18,343 --> 01:26:22,439
一两年内　你是很难了解这个镇的
In a year or two,
you're not gonna recognize this town.

1112
01:26:22,514 --> 01:26:25,642
噢　天啊
Oh, boy. Oh, boy!

1113
01:26:42,568 --> 01:26:45,002
你们这些杂种　我有你的资料
You sneaky son of a bitch!
I got your number now!

1114
01:26:45,070 --> 01:26:49,234
这些年来我以为你是个正人君子　我很感激你
All these years
I thought you were a decent man.
Ran around feeling grateful to you.

1115
01:26:49,308 --> 01:26:51,708
你相信吗　非常感激你
Can you believe that? Grateful!

1116
01:26:51,777 --> 01:26:54,405
好了你被炒了　他是利用我们
- You're fired!
- He's using us.

1117
01:26:54,479 --> 01:26:57,812
要我们做他的奴隶　你在做什么
- We're his slaves. We're alike.
- What were you doing with my truck?

1118
01:26:57,883 --> 01:27:02,911
你是懦夫吗　你完蛋了　把钥匙给我
- Are you a quitter? Quitter!
- You're finished. Gimme the keys.

1119
01:27:02,988 --> 01:27:05,115
我给你　我不受你管
I give it with pleasure.
I'm free of you.

1120
01:27:05,190 --> 01:27:08,785
我不会再回来这　你会看到是什么样了　不要碰我
- You're not on my back anymore.
You see how easy it is?
- Keep your hands off me.

1121
01:27:08,861 --> 01:27:14,493
我会处理　住手
I'll handle this.
Break it up. Break it up, Wade!

1122
01:27:14,566 --> 01:27:17,558
住手　韦德
Break it up! Wade!

1123
01:27:17,636 --> 01:27:21,265
我要修理你
You ain't gettin' away with this!
You ain't gettin' away with it!

1124
01:27:21,340 --> 01:27:24,969

Stay out of it, Jimmy. You're fired.
I want the shop keys. Where are they?

1125
01:27:25,043 --> 01:27:28,570
放开　走开
Wade, get out of here! Just go!

1126
01:27:28,647 --> 01:27:30,615
我打个电话给我弟弟
I gotta call my brother.

1127
01:27:37,522 --> 01:27:41,458
我知道那意思　我用尽我的方法
Yeah, I know what it means.
I'm just runnin' out of ways to use it.

1128
01:27:41,526 --> 01:27:44,393
为什么？为什么要帮助杰克
- Why? For what?
- To help Jack.

1129
01:27:44,463 --> 01:27:47,398
要将那群杂种绳之于法　两个乔丹
To nail those sons of bitches.
You know, the two Gordons.

1130
01:27:47,466 --> 01:27:51,402
艾玛就会那样叫他们的　鲁夫你支持谁
That's what Alma calls them.
Jesus, Rolfe, whose side are you on?

1131
01:27:51,470 --> 01:27:55,566
韦德　首先你小事要谨慎
Wade, listen.
Take care of the little things first,

1132
01:27:55,641 --> 01:27:59,077
那对你留意大事有帮助　
the things that are distracting you
from taking care of the big things.

1133
01:27:59,144 --> 01:28:01,578
打电话给美尼特　要回你的车
Call Chub Merritt,
get your car back.

1134
01:28:01,647 --> 01:28:04,582
打电话给牙医　拔掉烂牙
Call a dentist
and get your tooth pulled.

1135
01:28:04,650 --> 01:28:06,675
忘掉打猎意外不要管了
Forget about the hunting accident.

1136
01:28:06,752 --> 01:28:09,050
马上走
Let it go.

1137
01:28:12,357 --> 01:28:14,382
韦德
Wade?

1138
01:28:14,459 --> 01:28:19,021
好消息是我们还没有修好你的车
- Chick.
- The good news is,
we haven't got to your car yet.

1139
01:28:19,097 --> 01:28:22,032
那坏消息呢　告诉我什么时候修好
- The bad news...
- Just tell me when you have it fixed.

1140
01:28:22,100 --> 01:28:26,196
