01:47:33,117 --> 01:47:35,108

Ahh.

1318
01:47:57,475 --> 01:48:00,706
大家都知道这段历史真相
The historical facts
are known by everyone.

1319
01:48:00,778 --> 01:48:05,977
所有罗福特的居民　所有新汉普郡的人　一些马萨诸塞的人
All of Lawford, all of New Hampshire,
some of Massachusetts.

1320
01:48:06,050 --> 01:48:08,814
事实不能创造历史
Facts do not make history.

1321
01:48:08,886 --> 01:48:12,219
我们的故事　韦德和我的
Our stories, Wade's and mine,

1322
01:48:12,289 --> 01:48:16,749
描述了数千来来男孩和男人的生活
describe the lives of the boys and men
for thousands of years:

1323
01:48:16,827 --> 01:48:19,489
男孩被父亲殴打
Boys who were beaten
by their fathers,

1324
01:48:19,563 --> 01:48:23,932
出生那一天就抹杀了爱和信任能力
whose capacity for love and trust
was crippled almost at birth,

1325
01:48:24,001 --> 01:48:27,437
男人最好希望能联系其他人类
men whose best hope for connection
with other human beings...

1326
01:48:27,505 --> 01:48:29,439

lay in detachment...

1327
01:48:29,507 --> 01:48:32,135
好像生活完结了
as if life were over.

1328
01:48:32,209 --> 01:48:35,576
然后我们继续在毁灭下一代
It's how we keep from destroying
in turn our own children...

1329
01:48:35,646 --> 01:48:39,514
恐吓女人令她们不爱我们
and terrorizing the women
who have the misfortune to love us;

1330
01:48:39,583 --> 01:48:43,349
我们怎么打破男人的暴力传统
How we absent ourselves from
the tradition of male violence;

1331
01:48:43,420 --> 01:48:47,447
我们怎么拒绝得分的诱惑
How we decline
the seduction of revenge.

1332
01:48:47,525 --> 01:48:52,053
杰克的卡车三天后在多伦多购物广场外翻车
Jack's truck turned up three days later
in a shopping mall in Toronto.

1333
01:48:52,129 --> 01:48:55,394
韦德杀了杰克
Wade killed Jack...

1334
01:48:55,466 --> 01:48:59,459
肯定杰克没有杀汤比利
Just as surely as Jack
did not kill Evan Twombley,

1335
01:48:59,537 --> 01:49:02,097
即使是意外
even accidentally.

1336
01:49:02,173 --> 01:49:06,576
在杰克和汤比利　拉利维亚和梅尔乔丹之间
The link between Jack and Twombley,
LaRiviere and Mel Gordon...

1337
01:49:06,644 --> 01:49:09,977
只是韦德在他想象中存在
existed only
in Wade's wild imaginings.

1338
01:49:10,047 --> 01:49:13,710
简短的说　我承认我也一样
And briefly, I admit,
in mine as well.

1339
01:49:15,019 --> 01:49:19,285
拉利维亚和梅尔乔丹从事生意
LaRiviere and Mel Gordon
were indeed in business.

1340
01:49:19,356 --> 01:49:24,225
派克山滑雪胜地远近闻名
The Parker Mountain Ski Resort
is now advertised across the country.

1341
01:49:24,295 --> 01:49:27,890
罗福特社区不复存在了
The community of Lawford,
as such, no longer exists.

1342
01:49:27,965 --> 01:49:32,595
而是一个经济区
It is an economic zone
between Littleton and Catamount.

1343
01:49:32,670 --> 01:49:36,970
房子仍用韦德的名字　我来交税
The house is still in Wade's name,
and I keep paying taxes on it.

1344
01:49:37,041 --> 01:49:39,509
屋仍是空的
It remains empty.

1345
01:49:39,577 --> 01:49:43,035
我时不时路经这里　我坐在车里
Now and then I drive out there
and sit in my car,

1346
01:49:43,113 --> 01:49:45,877
想知道为什么不放弃它
and wonder why not let it go.

1347
01:49:45,950 --> 01:49:50,887
为什么不让拉利维亚买下它
Why not let LaRiviere buy it and
build the condominiums he wants there?

1348
01:49:52,289 --> 01:49:55,850
建立他的王国
We want to believe Wade died
that same November,

1349
01:49:55,926 --> 01:49:59,692
我们相信韦德同年十一月死了
froze to death on a bench
or a sidewalk.

1350
01:49:59,763 --> 01:50:02,231
在路边被冻死
You cannot understand
how a man,

1351
01:50:02,299 --> 01:50:06,235
你不能明白一个男人　一个和我们一样普通男人做这样的事
a normal man, a man like you and me,
could do such a terrible thing.

1352
01:50:08,472 --> 01:50:13,307
除非警察来这里拘捕流浪者
Unless the police happen
to arrest a vagrant who
turns out to be Wade Whitehouse,

1353
01:50:13,377 --> 01:50:16,744
就没有提及他的名字
there will be
no more mention of him.

1354
01:50:16,814 --> 01:50:19,942
还他的朋友杰克
Or his friend Jack Hewitt.

1355
01:50:20,017 --> 01:50:22,713
或者我们的父亲
Or our father.

1356
01:50:22,786 --> 01:50:25,721
本故事结束了
The story will be over,

1357
01:50:25,789 --> 01:50:29,350
等待我的故事发展
except that I continue.
